{"tid":1836920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有武漢旅客計劃經深圳轉車到香港探親","createTime":"2020-01-23T11:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T11:33:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92214f4ccc728d0fb0fea6c65307f0fe53ff444c","tid":1836920,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T11:30:54.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】不少乘客趕在武漢高鐵關閉離境通道前離開，部分人下午陸續抵達深圳，有武漢乘客透露，計劃去香港探親。<br />\n<br />\n在深圳北站，中午過後，由武漢開出的列車陸續到站，乘客都戴上口罩。<br />\n<br />\n由武漢乘高鐵去深圳車程要約五小時，有武漢居民透露，下一站計劃去香港。<br />\n<br />\n有婆婆帶同孫，由武漢回深圳探親。<br />\n<br />\n由武漢出發的高鐵，在早上十點鐘停運前有約17班開往深圳北站，不少乘客會選擇這個大站，再轉駁高鐵去其他地方，當中去香港的高鐵車程只需少於20分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n由深圳開往武漢的高鐵服務如常，但只會落客，不會上客。乘客指會在中途站下車， 但因為同車會有武漢人，都做好防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n高鐵站內大部分乘客都戴上口罩，多處都放置消毒酒精，而在高鐵站外，一批穿着全身防護裝備的人員，用儀器在四周噴灑消毒噴霧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=377855&amp;hot=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377855%26hot%3D1&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fpz4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=de01f586\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377855%26hot%3D1&h=2c9133a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=377855&amp;hot=1</a>"},{"pid":"ec5e16edfc2973b7986515eb135b320b378b77d1","tid":1836920,"uid":162095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T11:32:17.000Z","msg":"探少一年會死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你落嚟就真係分分鐘搞死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌"},{"pid":"d58f9dc78a8a9414636271ab2dce681a4f0b4fc3","tid":1836920,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T11:32:39.000Z","msg":"支持呀 政府唔封關即係歡迎啦"},{